flowchart TD
    A([Entry]) --> B[Def interval parameter]
    B --> C[Def interval via getReadableInterval]
    C --> D[P-use interval in overlaps method]
    D --> E{overlaps returns false?}
    E -- Yes --> F[Return null]
    E -- No --> G[Def start using max]
    G --> H[Def end using min]
    H --> I[C-use start and end in return Interval]
    I --> J([Exit])
    F --> J
